WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:15.000
舜天信兴样衣管理系统把设计样衣、大货样品、图片、借出、费用和 AI 能力放在同一个网页里。
The Sample Management System brings design samples, bulk samples, images, loans, fees, and AI tools into one web platform.

00:15.000 --> 00:30.000
右上角可以切换中文和 English；左侧进入设计部后台或业务前台。
The top-right switch toggles Chinese and English; the left side separates Design Admin from Sales Desk.

00:30.000 --> 00:45.000
业务员登录后，借样申请、PPT 记录和费用账单都会归到个人中心。
After sales sign-in, loan requests, PPT records, and fee bills are linked to the personal center.

00:45.000 --> 01:00.000
前台用瀑布流浏览，支持按样衣来源、在库、收藏和已选筛选。
The sales desk uses a waterfall browser with filters for source, availability, favorites, and selected items.

01:00.000 --> 01:15.000
搜索框右侧相机图标支持拍照或上传图片搜类似款。
The camera icon beside search supports photo or image upload for similar-style search.

01:15.000 --> 01:30.000
小爱心用于收藏并增加热度，勾选用于加入当前客户推款清单。
The heart favorites an item and raises its popularity count; the check mark adds it to the current pitch list.

01:30.000 --> 01:45.000
详情页查看正面、背面、价格、借样费、尺码、库位和近似款推荐。
The detail page shows front and back images, price, loan fee, size, location, and similar recommendations.

01:45.000 --> 02:00.000
多选样衣后，一键生成带图片和款式资料的推款 PPT。
After selecting samples, one click generates a pitch PPT with images and style information.

02:00.000 --> 02:15.000
设计部后台录入设计样衣和大货样品，AI 可快速补全字段。
Design Admin intakes design and bulk samples, and AI can quickly complete missing fields.

02:15.000 --> 02:30.000
AI 白底图、拍图搜款和报价功能帮助统一展示、检索同款并生成报价参考。
AI white-background images, visual search, and quoting help standardize presentation, find similar styles, and estimate prices.

02:30.000 --> 02:45.000
样衣管理员处理借出、归还和报损，费用按规则自动计算。
Administrators handle loans, returns, and loss reports, while fees are calculated by editable rules.

02:45.000 --> 03:00.000
后台按年、月、周和业务组拉取账单，并分析客户偏好与样衣准备方向。
Admin pulls bills by year, month, week, and team, then analyzes client demand for next-season preparation.
